  mutate(accuracy_pct = accuracy * 100) |&gt;
  gt() |&gt;
  cols_label(combo = "Condition", n_correct = "Correct",
             n_total = "Total", accuracy_pct = "Accuracy %") |&gt;
  fmt_number(columns = accuracy_pct, decimals = 1) |&gt;
  gt_theme_report()




Ablation Study
Components ranked by accuracy drop when removed. Larger drops indicate more important components.


